nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.items

Interface Item

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Pickupable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Chip, Exit, Info, Key

    public interface Item
    An item that can be on the board that actors can interact with. Items include key, chip, info, and exit. In order to be able to make instances of implementations of this implementations must have either a zero argument constructor or a public static build(Iteminfo) method.
